name: "Hodl" Cake - Salted Caramel Apple
description: @Sugartivi | Dear art collector, Hodl ("hold on for dear life") is a word I love because it’s not just about crypto. It’s an ethos for the unstable world we all live in now. As an ethos for life, it means understanding what’s really important & not giving it up. It means taking brave, smart risks and looking at the long term return. It also means hodling your nerve when people think you’re nuts. A series of 4 flavors, this one is inspired by taste memories from artists in the h=n community.
